        {
            "id": 6435753,
            "title": "OpenAI成長疑慮衝擊AI鏈供應鏈公司Oracle、CoreWeave盤前重挫",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><img alt=\"Reuters/TPG\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6435753/o/6bfcbdf714aaa226db08d1d864fc5235.jpg\"/></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"135\" data-start=\"38\">2026年04月28日（優分析／產業數據中心報導）⸺ AI概念股周二盤前走弱，主因市場傳出OpenAI近月新增用戶與營收表現未達目標，引發投資人對ChatGPT開發商成長前景與AI基礎設施需求的疑慮。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section><p data-end=\"206\" data-start=\"137\">據外電報導，OpenAI財務長Sarah Friar曾向公司高層表達憂慮，若營收成長速度不夠快，OpenAI未來支付運算合約的能力恐面臨壓力。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"296\" data-start=\"208\">受消息影響，Oracle(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ORCL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ORCL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ORCL-US</a>)盤前下跌近7%至161美元。Oracle據傳已與OpenAI簽署大型雲端合約，內容包括未來五年提供3000億美元運算能力。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"404\" data-start=\"298\">Nvidia(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>)投資的AI基礎設施公司CoreWeave(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRWV:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRWV\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRWV-US</a>)盤前下跌7.4%。該公司上月才與OpenAI簽署119億美元合約，將提供AI基礎設施服務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"492\" data-start=\"406\">CrossCheck Management投資長Todd Schoenberger表示，每當具有AI代表性的企業遭遇賣壓，市場往往會出現連鎖反應，不論相關跌勢是否完全合理。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"584\" data-start=\"494\">市場對OpenAI的審視升溫之際，該公司正為首次公開發行鋪路，潛在估值最高可達1 trillion美元。路透先前報導，OpenAI最快可能於2026年下半年向監管機構提交上市申請。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"744\" data-start=\"586\">OpenAI主要投資人軟銀集團SoftBank Group(9984-JP)東京股價收跌近10%，Arm Holdings(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ARM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ARM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ARM-US</a>)盤前下跌7.7%。軟銀先前承諾於2025年底前向OpenAI投入225億美元，並透過多項籌資安排支應資金需求，包括可能動用以Arm持股作為擔保的未提取保證金貸款。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"844\" data-start=\"746\">軟銀執行長孫正義近年大舉押注OpenAI，並透過出售Nvidia全部58億美元持股、處分T-Mobile(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TMUS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TMUS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TMUS-US</a>)48億美元持股，以及縮減人力來籌措資金。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"936\" data-start=\"846\">AI疑慮也拖累半導體族群。AMD(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMD-US</a>)、Broadcom(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AVGO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AVGO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AVGO-US</a>)與Nvidia盤前下跌3.2%至5.3%，三家公司均曾與OpenAI建立設備供應或投資合作關係。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p data-end=\"1068\" data-start=\"938\">本周大型科技股財報密集登場，Alphabet(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GOOGL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOGL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GOOGL-US</a>)、Microsoft(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MSFT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MSFT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MSFT-US</a>)、Meta Platforms(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:META:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/META\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">META-US</a>)與Amazon(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMZN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>)將陸續公布季度業績。市場將檢視AI資本支出能否轉化為足以支撐高估值的實際回報。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>※ 本文經「優分析」授權轉載，原文出處:<a href=\"https://uanalyze.com.tw/articles/7355351316\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color:#A9A9A9\">原文連結</a>\n<br/>※ 免責聲明：文中所提的個股、基金、期貨商品內容僅供參考，並非投資建議，投資人應獨立判斷，審慎評估風險。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p></p></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6435753",
